                            <comment id="14631417" author="philipthompson" created="Fri, 17 Jul 2015 14:41:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m getting &lt;tt&gt;InvalidRequest: code=2200 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;Invalid query&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; message=&quot;Attempted to set an element on a list which is null&quot;&lt;/tt&gt; instead, on the same operations.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=thobbs&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;thobbs&quot;&gt;thobbs&lt;/a&gt;, are these operations valid?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14631429" author="thobbs" created="Fri, 17 Jul 2015 14:55:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I think we recently changed the error message around that, which would explain why you are seeing a slightly different error.  Regardless, this should be working (especially since the same thing works for non-static columns), so it&apos;s definitely a bug.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
